---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Journal" subtitle="Tendencias & Noticias">
  <section class="py-32 bg-background">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <article class="group cursor-pointer">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-muted mb-6 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="text-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Mercado</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mt-2 mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            Tendencias del Mercado Inmobiliario en Rivas 2024
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground font-light text-sm line-clamp-2">
            Análisis completo de precios, demanda y proyecciones para el próximo año.
          </p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="group cursor-pointer">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-muted mb-6 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="text-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Consejos</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mt-2 mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            5 Errores que Cometen los Vendedores Primerizos
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground font-light text-sm line-clamp-2">
            Evite estos fallos comunes y maximice el valor de su propiedad.
          </p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="group cursor-pointer">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-muted mb-6 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="text-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Legal</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mt-2 mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            Nueva Ley de Vivienda: Lo que Necesita Saber
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground font-light text-sm line-clamp-2">
            Resumen de los cambios más importantes y cómo le afectan.
          </p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="group cursor-pointer">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-muted mb-6 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="text-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Inversión</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mt-2 mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            ¿Es Buen Momento para Invertir en Inmuebles?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground font-light text-sm line-clamp-2">
            Análisis de rentabilidad y oportunidades en el mercado actual.
          </p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="group cursor-pointer">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-muted mb-6 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="text-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Lifestyle</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mt-2 mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            Los Mejores Barrios de Rivas para Familias
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground font-light text-sm line-clamp-2">
            Guía completa con colegios, parques y servicios de cada zona.
          </p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="group cursor-pointer">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-muted mb-6 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="text-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Fiscalidad</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mt-2 mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            Impuestos al Vender: Guía Completa 2024
          </h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground font-light text-sm line-clamp-2">
            Todo sobre plusvalía, IRPF y deducciones disponibles.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
